Description: # Mucri
        
        Quickly fetch a lot of pages/apis using python `asyncio`.
        
        
        ## Installation
        
        > Only python 3.6+
        
        ```sh
        pip isntall mucri
        ```
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```python
        from mucri import fetch_links
        
        links = [
            "http://meain.github.io",
            { "url": "http://somelink" },
            {
                "url": "http://fakelink",
                "action": "get", # get | post
                "data": {},
                "headers": {},
                "resp_type": "text", # text | json
            }
        ]
        
        results = fetch_links(links) # fetches all of them asynchronously
        
        ```
        
